Merit in politics getting compromised by caste: K'taka Min.
Merit in politics is getting compromised by caste and loyalty to party leaders, said RV Deshpande, Minister for Large and Medium Industries in Karnataka, at the India Today Conclave South.The minister was replying to a question on how ministries are allocated in a government. RV Deshpande said that in his long political career he has also seen people from the grassroots going on to become highly successful ministers.